description: A kite the Traveler made under the guidance of Cloud Retainer. It captures Paimon being ill at ease, as though she was doing her utmost to explain: "Paimon totally hasn't been strung up here for doing something wrong..."\nIt's best to be forgiving on an auspicious day like Lantern Rite...
